PcData.name: <@>Venice{F}
PcData.biography: A natural leader, Venice prefers to lead from the thick of things, backing up her allies with blasts from her energy weapons.

PcData.name: <@>Houston{M}
PcData.biography: While his tendency to get into barroom brawls has caused problems in the past, Houston is still an incredible asset for any Ranger team.

PcData.name: <@>St. Petersburg{M}
PcData.biography: A dour and taciturn man, St. Petersburg is an expert at infiltration, demolitions, and long-range assassination.

PcData.name: <@>Kyoto{F}
PcData.biography: An expert marksman and master of bladed weaponry, Kyoto is an extremely valuable member of any Ranger team.

PcData.name: AZ3_Scotchmo_PC
PcData.biography: <@>Scotchmo is a former railway man from Rail Nomad who descended into alcoholism when his wife died. He says he drinks to forget, but it hasn't worked yet.

PcData.name: AZ1_SisterRose_PC
PcData.biography: <@>Rose doesn't say much about her past, except that she made a lot of mistakes and followed a lot of the wrong people. She has dedicated what's left of her life to making up for the sins of her youth.

PcData.name: AZ23_Vipula_PC
PcData.biography: <@>A young mutant woman who wants to escape the cloistered life of Darwin Village and see the world. Despite her strange looks and stranger upbringing, she has an open, engaging personality and an uncrushable sense of wonder.
